Class BinarySearchTreeDynamic

java.lang.Object
trees.BinarySearchTreeDynamic
All Implemented Interfaces:
BinarySearchTree
public class BinarySearchTreeDynamic
extends java.lang.Object
implements BinarySearchTree
A dynamic implementation of a Binary Search Tree(BST), where each Node holds information concerning it's right,left, parent linkage.
